[{"index":1,"title":"【小作】《雪下了...》","content":"多美的雪，由天际飘落，慢慢的...飘落在地上...\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;没有什么理想，只想着回归大地的怀抱，想着我自己，何时我才能回到大地...然而，你的飘落，你的覆盖曾经让我温暖...即使你是寒冷的雪花，我依旧期待着...你的再一次降临能够回到我的怀抱...可是...似乎不可能...\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;你回归了大地，化做白衣保护麦苗，化做雪水，与大地融合，滋润久以干涸的大地，当我回归时，只是化做一方尘土，依旧由你滋润，我真的离不开你吗？令我欣慰的是...我能够与你一起回归大地！\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;你飘落了，落在我的手心...瞬间化做一滴晶莹的水珠，像泪，像露，有种伤心得感觉，让人心悸...我不再在你身边了，遗忘了什么...我会找你...曾经飘落的雪，飘落到我身边...\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;什么时候，你才能再一次回来，纯洁的雪...我会再一次与你相遇吗？\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;好美的雪....\r<br>\u0018","author":"嘻哈の大呆","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2e2bf9d7.UI_mxvwa_6Mdp2Td2Hgfeg&fr=pb","date":"2006-12-31 22:19","ip":null,"old_image":"http://t3.baidu.com/it/u=950543873,727203969&gp=1.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【小作】《雪下了...》","content":"……\n继续~- -\n省略�","author":"月夜メ祭雪","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.8c31b28b.9CHxJcQLKtcn3GDqkoHZ4Q&fr=pb","date":"2006-12-31 22:23","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【小作】《雪下了...》","content":"^^\n…�","author":"雪￡魅儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec7c4b5f.KSJNpCIUJLOmFrJ1VJmBpQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-01-01 12:52","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【小作】《雪下了...》","content":"呆,今天新年,暂时忘记好么?","author":"T≌sea缘≌F","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.1e5f4dc9.PBD9sJ0rJ_OeH_E5DhThyg?t=1435627444&fr=pb","date":"2007-01-01 13:08","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【小作】《雪下了...》","content":"顶呆呆的�","author":"天奇轩羽·弈","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.99d84792.OVGY96T5mq8EDv3D5kwG5A&fr=pb","date":"2007-01-01 13:09","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【小作】《雪下了...》